{"type": "article", "id": 30052, "title": "大头钉小屋", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-24T22:51:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607242229584UhiMLVS78WuIjAk.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>除了钉在大头针板上，这些小文具也可以有别的去处：英国设计师以及工匠 <a href=\"http://www.cliveroddy.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Clive Roddy</a> 为它们设计了一个小屋，就像是从电影《飞屋环游记》中飞出来的迷你款。小屋的背面为钉子预留了一个开口便于固定，三根铁丝穿过圆柱形黄铜烟囱分别连接了一个球形软木，上面插有三百根大头针。用它来装点软木板或者是地图都能让人眼前一亮，只是放在办公桌上也非常有趣。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.cliveroddy.co.uk/shop/balloonpinhouse\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 25 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724223016TYP0kMdNvzw8nAVm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724223016x4nT8lPugB3qeH9M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724223016GanYypc1b0DoHTlM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607242230158ilUNgxy2zunRdbY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}